#

Coconut Lime Shrimp Tacos with Cabbage Slaw and Avocado Crema

$15.99
500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SeafoodTacosTropical Flavors

Description

Deliciously fresh coconut lime shrimp tacos topped with a crunchy cabbage slaw and creamy avocado, perfect for a light yet satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Coconut milk: 1/2 cup
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • Carrots: 1 cup, shredded
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Corn tortillas: 8
  • Avocado: 1
  • Greek yogurt (or dairy-free alternative): 1/4 cup
  • Garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
